{"tid":1468154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"盲講不割係毒 理性思考為優","createTime":"2019-08-13T18:00:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T10:08:43.000Z","uid":173466,"like":77,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"3ff43a75bbc175aabe981b396f66ee47b3833fce","tid":1468154,"uid":173466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:00:24.000Z","msg":"先唔講有無鬼，大家每做一個決定應該出於理性。<br />\n<br />\n盲講唔割，[black]<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">將唔割口號化根本係毒，搞到大家無理性</span></span>[/black]<br />\n<br />\n好簡單，如果我係鬼既話，我都會瘋狂講唔割，捆綁大家去跟佢地劇本行，有鬼你又唔知，咁你同隻鬼又唔割，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁你即係同隻鬼一家親</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n我唔係講點捉鬼，我想講<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">每個人都應該理性思考，有理性就唔可以割，唔理性就要指出，盲講唔割即係幫緊鬼</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n同意請幫推"},{"pid":"ee2a09e70968d26c0c58445476bf70b7d8fe3f9d","tid":1468154,"uid":95487,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:00:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有<br />\n唔會捉得晒<br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ec032c2090cc859db5bf4ffbce0ce19e675258","tid":1468154,"uid":173466,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ee2a09e70968d26c0c58445476bf70b7d8fe3f9d","tid":1468154,"uid":95487,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:00:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有<br />\n唔會捉得晒<br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:02:01.000Z","msg":"有無鬼都要理性，行動前先諗有咩效果同目的"},{"pid":"78cd8ff2cb76ce8248b0edec8df155ee71c17dac","tid":1468154,"uid":173466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:02:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ab26a20929b286511ff1d527286052862a99f7c","tid":1468154,"uid":173466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:03:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4fc10678e4f9245a9b43516210a68a2fd5fd8697","tid":1468154,"uid":173466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T1